# 🔗 Cross-Module Correlation Map

```
Bag.AddItem ──publish──▶ "item.added" ──┬──▶ Task.onItemAdded       (progress +1, ignores count)
                                         ├──▶ Achievement.onItemAdded (checks unlocked ach count for collector_100)
                                         └──▶ Equipment.onItemAdded   (auto-equip if itemID ∈ {3001,3002})
                                               │
                                               └──▶ "equip.success" ──▶ Achievement.onEquipSuccess (weapon+armor → fully_equipped)

Task.Progress ──(when target met)──▶ "task.completed" ──▶ Achievement.onTaskCompleted (maps task→ach, unlocks)

Achievement.Unlock ──▶ "achievement.unlocked" ──▶ Mail.onAchievementUnlocked (sends mail, NO attachment)

SignIn.CheckIn ──▶ "signin.claimed" ──▶ Mail.onSignInClaimed (sends mail WITH attachment)

SignIn.ClaimReward ──▶ "signin.reward" ──▶ ⚠️ NO SUBSCRIBER

Mail.ClaimAttachment ──▶ "mail.claimed" ──▶ ⚠️ NO SUBSCRIBER (items never reach bag)

Equipment.Equip ──▶ "equip.success" (no bag consumption, no item validation)
Equipment.Unequip ──▶ "equip.unequipped" (no bag return)
```

